Title: Practical Magic
Writer: Alice Hoffman (novel), Robin Swicord (screenplay), Akiva Goldsman (screenplay), Adam Brooks (screenplay)
Actors: Sandra Bullock, Nicole Kidman, Stockard Channing, Dianne Wiest
Plot: Two witch sisters, raised by their eccentric aunts in a small town, face closed-minded prejudice and a curse which threatens to prevent them ever finding lasting love.
Production: Warner Brothers, DiNovi Pictures, Fortis Films
